properties.name: Cabalen
properties.description: Cabalen is famous for reasonably priced buffet food-serving in an atmosphere of Filipino festivity and dinner table abundance. With a mere P220 (just more than $4) per head (drinks not included) we get to enjoy a feast of assorted and delicately cooked luscious native dishes and treats. Everything is set to create a banqueting experience right in grandma's dining hall and kitchen at CabalenManila's pride in Pampanga culinary specialties.

properties.description: Gerry's Grill provides everyone and anyone who loves to eat with fresh food that is cooked, grilled, or prepared to satisfy the most distinguishing of palates. Ultimately, every item on the menu goes perfectly well with your favorite beverage; whether it be alcoholic or not. For a full meal with the family or for a night-out with the boys or girls, Gerry's Grill offers the perfect place with the perfect menu to fit any occasion at any budget.
